<div style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #222;">
  <h2 style="margin:0 0 12px; color: #e74c3c;">‚ö†Ô∏è Trial Ending Soon</h2>
  <p>Hi <%= garage_name %>,</p>
  <p>
    Your free trial for the <strong><%= plan_name %></strong> plan is ending soon!
  </p>
  
  <div style="background: #f8f9fa; border-left: 4px solid #e74c3c; padding: 16px; margin: 16px 0;">
    <h3 style="margin: 0 0 8px; color: #e74c3c;">Trial Details:</h3>
    <ul style="margin: 0; padding-left: 20px;">
      <li><strong>Plan:</strong> <%= plan_name %></li>
      <li><strong>Price:</strong> <%= price_formatted %> per month</li>
      <li><strong>Trial ends:</strong> <%= trial_end_date %></li>
      <li><strong>Days remaining:</strong> <span style="color: #e74c3c; font-weight: bold;"><%= days_remaining %></span></li>
    </ul>
  </div>

  <p>
    <strong>What happens next?</strong><br/>
    After your trial ends, you'll be automatically charged <strong><%= price_formatted %></strong> per month to continue using our services.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Want to continue?</strong><br/>
    No action needed! Your subscription will automatically continue after the trial period.
  </p>

  <p>
    <strong>Want to cancel or update payment method?</strong><br/>
    You can manage your subscription anytime through our billing portal:
  </p>
  
  <% if (billing_portal_url) { %>
  <p>
    <a href="<%= billing_portal_url %>" style="background:#2d6cdf;color:#fff;padding:12px 24px;text-decoration:none;border-radius:4px;display:inline-block;margin:8px 0;">Manage Subscription</a>
  </p>
  <% } %>

  <div style="background: #e8f4fd; border: 1px solid #bee5eb; padding: 12px; margin: 16px 0; border-radius: 4px;">
    <p style="margin: 0; font-size: 14px; color: #0c5460;">
      <strong>üí° Pro Tip:</strong> Update your payment method now to avoid any service interruption when your trial ends.
    </p>
  </div>

  <p>
